step 1:
open index.html, then open user1.html and user2.html
Step 2:
run redis server:
redis-server
step 3:
run 2 different backend instance from two different terminal:
./gradlew bootRun --args='--server.port=8080'
./gradlew bootRun --args='--server.port=8081'
step 4:
open user1.html and user2.html
step 5:
click connect and join on both page
step 6:
click correct answer or incorrect answer on both page
step 7:
watch the leaderboard update in real-time on both page
